      "writtenOn": "2021-03-16T19:11:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So dmsaa is really experimental right now, but the main idea here was to lift some optimizations from attemptQuadOptimization to the SkGpuDevice level to make sure we still get them when the dmsaa codepaths don\u0027t go through attemptQuadOptimization. This is mainly to get fewer diffs in gold, and it\u0027s also why I put it behind the fSurfaceIsDMSAA flag for now, but if it\u0027s too immature at this point we don\u0027t have to land.",
